Usage: --base BASE_JSONL --diff DIFF_JSONL [--report-path REPORT_PATH]

Available options:
        --base <BASE_JSONL>  JSONL artifact for the **base** side of the comparison (typically an
                `elp lint --format=json` run at a prior project state). Diagnostics present here but
                missing on the diff side are reported as removed.
        --diff <DIFF_JSONL>  JSONL artifact for the **diff** side of the comparison (typically an
                `elp lint --format=json` run at the current project state). Diagnostics present here
                but missing on the base side are reported as new.
        --report-path <REPORT_PATH>  Optional path to write the Markdown comparison report (headline
                counts + per-(diagnostic, severity) summary table) to. When omitted, the report is
                written to stdout.
    -h, --help  Prints help information
